      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 110,
      "message": "this should better be after `RuN chown` below, because the chown op will double the docker image size.\n\nthus, we can have:\n\nRUN chown $user:$group /tmp/vid /usr/local/tomcat -R\nCOPY  --chown=$user:$group --from=build /vid /usr/local/tomcat/webapps/vid/",
